snippet.textDisplay:
I love StarFox, shame the series is in a bit of a mess. I really enjoyed StarFox DS despite it's negative reception. Sure, it took a while getting used to the turn-based strategy layout but it was the same layout planned for StarFox II (Unreleased). Assault was alright, though there were many lame parts.

Interesting fact: None of the StarFox crew have legs! They have metal prosthetic limbs due to Arwing speed causing blood clots. (Don't believe me? Look at Fox's legs on the boxart!)
snippet.textOriginal:
